reviews.review_text: Good stuff Great year! saw them at RFK STADIUM.  Hey at least Im enjoying the ride !
Hult This is a fine show. Jerry in great voice, just listen to him on Black Peter. Very nice. Clear in your face board

Loved the Hult Had a great time at these shows as well as '83..typically great transfer.  And by the way anybody who says the Dead played at RFK in '84 is simply clueless.  They played Merriweather and it was incredible.

Fair Show Nothing over the top, standard.
No Highlights
